: null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013904, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "When you intend to bid farewell one should stand at the head, lament and recite…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jab rauze par se aakhri rukhsati ka iraada ho, to sar ki jaanib khade ho kar girya karte huwe kahe…", "UrduDescription": "جب تک چاہے حضرتؑ کے پاس رہے لیکن بہتر یہ ہے کہ اس مقدس جگہ کو اپنی خواب گاہ نہ بنائے۔ جب حضرت امام حسینؑ سے وداع کرنا چاہے تو آپ کے سرہانے کے نزدیک کھڑا ہو جائے اور روتے ہوئے کہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013905, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be on you, O my Master! This is the farewell salutation of the departing visitor, neither due to lack of interest, nor on account of fatigue; and if I go back, it is not because of uneasiness; and if I stay, it is not in view of the tempting persuasion which Allah has set forth for those who endure. O my Master! May Allah let not my this visit to you be the last one, but enable me to come back here again and again, visit your holy Haram and be near your resting abode. So let it be, O Lord of the worlds.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aap par salaam ho ay mere Aaqa wida karne waale ka, salaam uska jo dil tang nahi aur na thaka huwa hai, pas agar mai palat jaawu to uski wajah ranjish nahi aur agar thairu to uski wajah bad-gumaani nahi. Is wida se jo Khuda ne saabiro’n se kiya hai mere Aaqa Khuda is ziyarat ko mere liye aakhri ziyarat qaraar na de, woh mujhe aap ke huzoor dobaara aana naseeb kare, aap ke haram mein thaiyr ne ka mauqa de aur aap ke rauze par haazri ki saadat bakhshe, aisa hi ho ay jahano ke Rab.", "Urdu": "آپ پر سلام ہو اے میرے آقا وداع کرنے والے کا سلام اس کا جو دل تنگ نہیں اور نہ تھکا ہوا ہے پس اگر میں پلٹ جاؤں تو اس کی وجہ رنجش نہیں اور اگر ٹھہروں تو اس کی وجہ بد گمانی نہیں اس وعدے سے جو خدا نے صابروں سے کیا ہے اے میرے آقا خدا اس زیارت کو میرے لئے آخری زیارت قرار نہ دے وہ مجھے آپ کے حضور دوبارہ آنا نصیب کرے آپ کے حرم میں ٹھہرنے کا موقع دے اور آپ کے روضہ پر حاضری کی سعادت بخشے ایسا ہی ہو اے جہانوں کے رب۔", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA MAWLAAYA SALAAMA MOO-DE-I’N LAA QAALA WA LAA SA-EMIN FA-IN ANSARIF FALAA A’N MALAALATIN WA IN O-QIM FALAA A’N SOO-E ZANNIM BEMAA WA-A’DAL LAAHUS SAABEREENA YAA MAWLAAYA LAA JA-A’LAHUL LAAHO AAKHERAL A’HDE MINNEE LE-ZEYAARATEKA WA RAZAQANIL A’WDA ILAIKA WAL MAQAAMA FEE KARAMEKA WAL-KAWNA FEE MASH-HADEKA AAMEENA RABBAL A’ALAMEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا مَوْلَایَ سَلَامَ مُوَدِّعٍ لَا قَالٍ وَلَا سَئِمٍ فَاِنْ اَنْصَرِفْ فَلَا عَنْ مَلَالَۃٍ وَاِنْ اُقِمْ فَلَا عَنْ سُوْٓءِ ظَنٍّ بِمَا وَعَدَ اللہُ الصَّابِرِیْنَ یَا مَوْلَایَ لَا جَعَلَهُ اللہُ آخِرَ الْعَهْدِ مِنِّیْ لِزِیَارَتِكَ وَرَزَقَنِی الْعَوْدَ اِلَیْكَ وَالْمَقَامَ فِیْ كَرَمِكَ وَالْكَوْنَ فِیْ مَشْهَدِكَ اٰمِیْنَ رَبَّ الْعَالَمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013906, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Then kiss the zareeh and touch your whole body to it, indeed this grants safety. Come out in such a way that the grave is to the front and do not turn your back to the grave and then recite…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Phir Zareeh-e-muqaddas ko bosa de aur apne saare badan ko zareeh se mas kare, keh be-shak yeh uske liye hifz o amaan ka baais hai. Phir qabre mubarak ke yahan se nikal pade lekin is tarah, keh uska chehra qabr ki taraf ho aur pusht qabr ki taraf na kare us waqt yeh kahe…", "UrduDescription": "اب حضرت امام حسینؑ کی ضریح مقدس کوبوسہ دے اور اپنے سارے بدن کو اس سے مس کرے کہ بے شک یہ اس کے لئے حفظ و امان کا باعث ہے پھر حضرت امام حسینؑ کے ہاں سے نکل پڑے لیکن اس طرح کہ اس کا منہ قبر کی طرف ہو او رپشت اس کی طرف نہ کرے اس وقت یہ کہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013907, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be on you, O he at whose door all the faithfuls come to seek peace. Peace be on you, O he who is the part and parcel of the Holy Qur’an. Peace be on you, O he who is an evident proof of Allah for the antagonists. Peace be on you, O he who is the ark of salvation. Peace be on (all of) you, O Angels of my Lord, quartered in this Holy precinct. Peace be on you, forever, so far I am alive, and days and nights follow each other.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aap par salaam ho ay ahle imaan ke maqaam ke darwaaze. Aap par salaam ho ay ham martaba Qur’an. Aap par salaam ho ay dushmano par hujjat. Aap par salaam ho ay kashtiye najaat. Aap par salaam ho ay mere Rab ke farishto jo us haram mein iqamat rakhte (rehte) hai. Salaam ho aap par hamesha hamesha jab tak mai baaqi hu aur raat din baaqi hai.", "Urdu": "آپ پر سلام ہو اے اہل ِایمان کے مقام کے دروازہ، آپ پر سلام ہو اے ہم مرتبۂ قرآن، آپ پر سلام ہو اے دشمنوں پر حجت، آپ پر سلام ہو اے کشتی نجات آپ پر سلام ہو اے میرے رب کے فرشتو جو اس حرم میں مقیم ہیں سلام ہو آپ پر ہمیشہ ہمیشہ جب تک میں باقی ہوں اور رات دن باقی ہیں۔", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA BAABAL MAQAAME AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA SHAREEKAL QUR-AAANE AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA HUJJATAL KHESAAME AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA SAFEENATAN NAJAATE AS-SALAAMO A’LAYKUM YAA MALAAA-EKATA RABBIL MOQEEMEENA FEE HAAZAL HARAME AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA ABADAM MAA BAQEETO WA BAQEYAL LAYLO WAN-NAHAARO.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا بَابَ الْمَقَامِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا شَرِیْكَ الْقُرْآنِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا حُجَّۃَ الْخِصَامِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا سَفِیْنَۃَ النَّجَاۃِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكُمْ یَا مَلَآئِكَۃَ رَبِّیْ الْمُقِیْمِیْنَ فِیْ هٰذَا الْحَرَمِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ اَبَدًا مَّا بَقِیْتُ وَبَقِیَ اللَّیْلُ وَالنَّهَارُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "Ar